---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Paid Search (SEA) Services | OnlineMarketingCORE">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Paid Search Marketing Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Drive targeted traffic, generate qualified leads, and maximize ROI with our data-driven paid search services.
      </p>
      <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Placeholder for PPC campaign SVG -->
        <div class="bg-gray-200 h-64 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-gray-500">PPC Campaign SVG Illustration</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Service Description Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Paid Search Approach</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          At OnlineMarketingCORE, we deliver high-performing paid search campaigns that connect your business with users actively searching for products or services like yours. Our data-driven methodology ensures measurable results and continuous improvement.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          With over 25 years of experience, our team of certified specialists creates custom-tailored strategies across multiple ad platforms to help you achieve your business goals, whether that's increasing sales, generating leads, or building brand awareness.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Benefits Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Key Benefits & Outcomes</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Immediate Visibility</h3>
            <p>Unlike organic methods, paid search delivers immediate visibility for your business, allowing you to start generating traffic from day one.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Precision Targeting</h3>
            <p>Target customers based on search intent, location, device, demographics, and more to ensure your budget is spent reaching the most valuable prospects.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Measurable Results</h3>
            <p>Track every impression, click, and conversion with detailed analytics that show exactly how your investment translates into business results.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Scalable Growth</h3>
            <p>Easily scale your campaigns up or down based on performance, seasonality, or business goals, ensuring maximum flexibility.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Platforms Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Paid Search Platforms We Specialize In</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <a href="./paid-search/google-ads" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Google Ads Logo</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Google Ads</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Reach the world's largest search audience with targeted campaigns on Google's advertising platform.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          <a href="./paid-search/display-ads" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Display Ads Logo</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Display Advertising</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Build brand awareness and retarget potential customers with visual ads across the web.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          <a href="./paid-search/video-ads" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Video Ads Logo</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Video Advertising</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Engage your audience with compelling video content on YouTube and partner networks.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          <a href="./paid-search/shopping-ads" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Shopping Ads Logo</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Shopping Ads</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Showcase your products directly in search results with detailed product information.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          <a href="./paid-search/microsoft-ads" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Microsoft Ads Logo</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Microsoft Advertising</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Reach the Bing, Yahoo, and DuckDuckGo search networks with targeted campaigns.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
          <a href="./paid-search/social-ads" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 h-32 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-gray-500">Social Ads Logo</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Social Media Advertising</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Leverage the targeting capabilities of social platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and LinkedIn.</p>
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Learn More →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process Breakdown Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Paid Search Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Account Structure SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Account Structure SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Account Structure</h3>
              <p>We design a strategic account structure that aligns with your business goals, organizing campaigns, ad groups, and keywords for optimal performance and management efficiency.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Keyword Research SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Keyword Research SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Keyword Research</h3>
              <p>Our thorough keyword research identifies high-intent search terms with optimal volume, competition, and relevance to your offerings, incorporating both commercial and informational queries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Ad Creative SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Ad Creative SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Ad Creative Development</h3>
              <p>We craft compelling ad copy and extensions that highlight your unique value propositions, implementing A/B testing to continuously refine messaging and improve click-through rates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Landing Page SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Landing Page SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Landing Page Optimization</h3>
              <p>We analyze and enhance landing pages to ensure they deliver a seamless user experience and compelling conversion points that align with ad messaging, maximizing Quality Score and conversion rates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Performance Monitoring SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Performance Monitoring SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Performance Monitoring</h3>
              <p>Our continuous monitoring and optimization process includes bid adjustments, budget allocation refinements, audience targeting improvements, and negative keyword expansion to enhance campaign performance over time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Case Studies Preview Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Success Stories</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">E-Commerce Revenue Growth</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">A leading online retailer achieved a 135% increase in ROAS (Return on Ad Spend) through our strategic keyword restructuring and enhanced product feed optimization.</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Read Case Study →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">B2B Lead Generation</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Our account restructuring and landing page optimization helped a software company reduce cost-per-lead by 42% while increasing qualified lead volume by 28%.</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Read Case Study →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">What is the difference between SEO and paid search?</h3>
            <p>SEO (Search Engine Optimization) focuses on improving organic (unpaid) visibility in search results, which takes time to build but provides long-term benefits. Paid search delivers immediate visibility through paid placements but requires ongoing investment. Many businesses benefit from a combined approach.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How do you determine the right paid search budget?</h3>
            <p>We analyze factors including your industry, competition level, geographic targeting, business goals, and current performance data to recommend an appropriate budget that balances reach with ROI. We can adapt budgets based on performance and seasonality.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Which paid search platforms should my business use?</h3>
            <p>The optimal platform mix depends on your target audience, industry, and goals. Google Ads offers the largest reach, but Microsoft Advertising may provide better ROI in certain B2B sectors, while social platforms excel for highly targeted demographic campaigns. We'll recommend the most effective combination for your specific needs.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How long does it take to see results from paid search?</h3>
            <p>Unlike SEO, paid search can generate immediate traffic once campaigns are launched. However, optimization for peak performance typically takes 2-4 weeks as we gather data and refine targeting, messaging, and bidding strategies.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How do you measure paid search success?</h3>
            <p>We establish clear KPIs aligned with your business goals, which may include ROAS, cost per acquisition, conversion rate, or lead quality. Our reporting provides transparent performance metrics and actionable insights into campaign effectiveness.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-blue-700 text-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to transform your paid search performance?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8">Schedule a free consultation with our paid search experts to discuss your goals and discover how we can help.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="inline-block py-3 px-8 bg-white text-blue-700 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">Book Your Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout> 
